      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Prepared to overlook the latest result of IM THE FALCON NZ (4) as he drew poorly and had to work. Has finished top-three in his other three starts since joining Chantal Turpin for this campaign, highlighted by a win at this circuit and distance two back. A better draw can see him back in the winners' list. TIMS A TROOPER (7) continues to perform strongly, racing up to four wide when winning over this distance two back before missing a smart one by just a head last week. Draws wide but was runner-up from this barrier last month and the recent consistency is hard to knock. FRANKIE FEROCIOUS (5) overcame a 30m handicap to win when off a let-up here last time and got within a nose of TIMS A TROOPER prior. Contender. A return to the front row brings JIMARTEE (3) into contention.",
